      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by my doctor a few days ago here in sydney and the cut is looking a bit weird. its kind of red and feels warm to the touch and there is some yellow stuff oozing out of it slightly. do u think i should just put a warm compress on it and some antibiotic cream from the chemist and let it heal itself? i really dont want to have to go back to the clinic if i dont have to",
